abstract: Los Angeles County officials say they will examine cellphone records of Bruce Jenner and other drivers who were involved in multivehicle accident on Pacific Coast Highway that resulted in death of woman Kim Howe and injured seven others; investigators will try to determine if drivers were texting before crash.
lead_paragraph: Investigators are likely to seek data for all of the drivers involved in the multivehicle accident, including Bruce Jenner, that left one dead in California.

headline.main: Authorities May Check Calls and Texts in Jenner Crash
headline.print_headline: Officials May Check Texts of Drivers in Jenner Crash
